Summary
-------

Creates a distinct environment for each language, where people will only see pages in the current language.
Can be configured via the "localized_pages" flag of the site. Currently there's no UI.

Installation
------------

Generate the migration:

  script/generate plugin_migration localized_pages

Migrate the database:

  rake db:migrate


